Then, she released her second album "+1" which contained all her single since from 2016 and 2017 and five new songs, most of the singles became or were already big radio hits.
All those song became huge radio hits, except "Halb või hea" they all reached 500k listening on Spotify, "Kehakeel" being her most listened song ever with 820k listening as of November 2021.
In 2021, she signed with Warner Music and released the song "Magusvalus".
